AUDITION ANALYTICS
==================

Track voice acting auditions across Voice123, ACX, and Casting Call Club.
Voice123 data is scraped automatically; ACX and CCC can be entered manually.


SETUP
-----

1. Install dependencies:

     pip install -r requirements.txt
     playwright install chromium

2. Copy and fill in your credentials:

     cp config.example.json config.json

3. Authenticate with Voice123 (one time — saves session to .v123_session.json):

     python scraper.py --headed

   Log in normally in the browser that opens, then press Enter in the terminal.

4. Start the server:

     python server.py

   App runs at http://localhost:5002


SCRAPING
--------

After the first login, run headlessly:

     python scraper.py

To force re-authentication (e.g. when session expires):

     python scraper.py --login


SCHEDULED SCRAPING (Ubuntu server)
-----------------------------------

Add to crontab (crontab -e) to run every 6 hours:

     0 */6 * * * cd /path/to/audition-analytics && python scraper.py >> scraper.log 2>&1

Or use a systemd timer — see your system's documentation.


NOTES
-----

- Voice123 selectors in scraper.py may need adjustment if Voice123 updates
  their markup. All selectors are in the SELECTORS section at the top of the file.
- Scraper does upsert: existing records get their viewed/liked/booked status
  updated; new auditions are inserted.
- ACX and CCC auditions can be added manually via the "+ add audition" button
  in the Log tab.
